You can create  your own AppImages and .deb files, just ask ChatGPT to write a script for it.
Provide a link too.


"Disable the kitty protocol in fish shell (5u)" [works for Cool-Retro-Term as well]
set -Ux fish_features no-keyboard-protocols


"lxappearance saves its files in:"
/home/mint/.local/share

"and the custom settings in:"
/home/mint/.config/gtk-3.0


"For Rofi"
Instead of changing the .css file, just change any of the .sh files included with the themes and link its directory path to use it.


